# Implementation Strategy: Auto-Location for WooCommerce

> **Approach**: 5 phases over ~6–8 weeks, each phase independently deployable. Each phase results in a working, testable plugin version before the next phase begins.

---

## Phase Overview & Timeline

```mermaid
gantt
    title ALW Plugin Improvement Roadmap
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD
    axisFormat  %b %d

    section Phase 1: Security
    P0 Security Fixes              :p1, 2026-03-21, 4d

    section Phase 2: WC Architecture
    Proper Shipping Method + HPOS  :p2, after p1, 5d

    section Phase 3: Code Quality
    i18n + JS Externalize + Cleanup :p3, after p2, 5d

    section Phase 4: Advanced Features
    Distance Tiers + Zones + Admin Map :p4, after p3, 7d

    section Phase 5: Future-Proofing
    WC Blocks + Multi-Store        :p5, after p4, 7d
```

| Phase | Focus | Est. Effort | Cumulative Timeline |
|-------|-------|-------------|---------------------|
| **1** | Security Hardening | 3–4 days | Week 1 |
| **2** | WooCommerce Architecture Compliance | 4–5 days | Week 2 |
| **3** | Code Quality & i18n | 4–5 days | Week 3 |
| **4** | Advanced Features | 5–7 days | Week 4–5 |
| **5** | Future-Proofing | 5–7 days | Week 6–8 |

