## Phase 1: Security Hardening — `v1.3.0`

> [!CAUTION]
> This phase fixes an exploitable pricing vulnerability. Deploy first.

### 1.1 Server-Side Distance Verification

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-shipping.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php)

**Current**: Backend trusts `$_POST['billing_distance']` as highest priority.

**Change**: Invert the priority — always compute server-side distance first, use frontend value only as a cross-check or fallback hint.

```diff
- // Priority 1: Use the Frontend Distance (Driving) if available
- if ( $cust_dist > 0 ) {
-     $distance_km = $cust_dist;
- }
- // Priority 2: Backend Calculation (Fail-safe)
- else {
+ // ALWAYS compute server-side distance
+ $dir = $this->get_directions_distance( ... );
+ if ( $dir && isset( $dir['distance_km'] ) ) {
+     $distance_km = (float) $dir['distance_km'];
+ } else {
+     $distance_km = $this->get_haversine_km( ... );
+ }
```

Apply the same change to [validate_distance_limit()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#78-112).

### 1.2 API Key Security Guidance

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-admin.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-admin.php)

- Add a warning notice below the API Key field advising the admin to restrict the key to their domain (HTTP referrer restriction) and limit it to only the 4 required APIs.
- Change the input type from [text](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-admin.php#83-88) to `password` so the key is masked by default.

### 1.3 Settings Sanitization

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-admin.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-admin.php)

Add `sanitize_callback` to every [register_setting()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-admin.php#33-54) call:

| Setting | Sanitizer |
|---------|-----------|
| `alw_google_api_key` | `sanitize_text_field` |
| `alw_store_lat` | Custom: validate float, range `-90` to `90` |
| `alw_store_lng` | Custom: validate float, range `-180` to `180` |
| `alw_free_km` | `absint` or custom: non-negative float |
| `alw_max_km` | Custom: non-negative float, must be ≥ `free_km` |
| `alw_rate_per_km` | Custom: non-negative float |
| `alw_round_method` | Custom: whitelist `ceil`, `floor`, `round` |

### 1.4 Uninstall Cleanup

#### [NEW] [uninstall.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/uninstall.php)

```php
<?php
if ( ! defined( 'WP_UNINSTALL_PLUGIN' ) ) exit;
// Delete all plugin options
$options = ['alw_google_api_key','alw_store_lat','alw_store_lng','alw_free_km','alw_max_km','alw_rate_per_km','alw_round_method'];
foreach ( $options as $opt ) delete_option( $opt );
// Clean up transients (ds_dir_*, ds_geo_*)
global $wpdb;
$wpdb->query( "DELETE FROM {$wpdb->options} WHERE option_name LIKE '_transient_ds_dir_%' OR option_name LIKE '_transient_timeout_ds_dir_%' OR option_name LIKE '_transient_ds_geo_%' OR option_name LIKE '_transient_timeout_ds_geo_%'" );
```

