## Phase 2: WooCommerce Architecture Compliance — `v1.4.0`

### 2.1 Proper WC_Shipping_Method Integration

#### [NEW] [class-alw-shipping-method.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping-method.php)

Create a new class `ALW_Shipping_Method extends WC_Shipping_Method` that:
- Declares `$this->id = 'alw_distance_shipping'`
- Appears in **WooCommerce → Settings → Shipping → Shipping Zones**
- Implements `calculate_shipping( $package )` using the existing distance logic from [ALW_Shipping_Calculator](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#4-184)
- Supports instance settings (rate per km, free km, max km) so different zones can have different rules

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-shipping.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php)

Refactor into a **helper/service class** (`ALW_Distance_Service`) that the shipping method calls. Keep [validate_distance_limit()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#78-112) and the helper methods ([get_directions_distance](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#137-161), [geocode_address](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#162-183), [get_haversine_km](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#128-136)) here.

#### [MODIFY] [auto-location-woocommerce.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/auto-location-woocommerce.php)

Register the shipping method via `woocommerce_shipping_methods` filter:

```php
add_filter( 'woocommerce_shipping_methods', function( $methods ) {
    $methods['alw_distance_shipping'] = 'ALW_Shipping_Method';
    return $methods;
});
```

### 2.2 HPOS Compatibility Declaration

#### [MODIFY] [auto-location-woocommerce.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/auto-location-woocommerce.php)

```php
add_action( 'before_woocommerce_init', function() {
    if ( class_exists( \Automattic\WooCommerce\Utilities\FeaturesUtil::class ) ) {
        \Automattic\WooCommerce\Utilities\FeaturesUtil::declare_compatibility( 'custom_order_tables', __FILE__, true );
    }
});
```

### 2.3 WooCommerce Dependency Check

#### [MODIFY] [auto-location-woocommerce.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/auto-location-woocommerce.php)

Add an activation/runtime check that WooCommerce is active before loading any plugin logic. Display a dismissible admin notice if WC is not found.

