## Phase 3: Code Quality & Internationalization — `v1.5.0`

### 3.1 Externalize JavaScript

#### [NEW] [alw-checkout-map.js](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/assets/js/alw-checkout-map.js)

Move the 520+ line JS from the Heredoc in [class-alw-frontend.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-frontend.php) into this external file. Replace template placeholders with `wp_localize_script()`:

```php
wp_enqueue_script( 'alw-checkout-map', plugins_url('assets/js/alw-checkout-map.js', dirname(__FILE__)), ['jquery'], $ver, true );
wp_localize_script( 'alw-checkout-map', 'alw_config', [
    'api_key'      => ALW_GOOGLE_API_KEY,
    'store_lat'    => ALW_STORE_LAT,
    'store_lng'    => ALW_STORE_LNG,
    'free_km'      => ALW_FREE_KM,
    'max_km'       => ALW_MAX_KM,
    'rate_per_km'  => ALW_RATE_PER_KM,
    'round_method' => ALW_ROUND_METHOD,
    'currency'     => get_woocommerce_currency_symbol(),
]);
```

#### [NEW] [alw-checkout-blocker.js](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/assets/js/alw-checkout-blocker.js)

Move the blocking script from [output_blocking_script()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-frontend.php#50-145) into this external file.

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-frontend.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-frontend.php)

- Remove the [get_map_js_template()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-frontend.php#146-670) Heredoc method entirely
- Remove [output_blocking_script()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-frontend.php#50-145) inline `<script>` tag
- Enqueue both new JS files via `wp_enqueue_scripts`
- Significant reduction from ~670 lines to ~80 lines

### 3.2 JS Namespace Consolidation

In the new `alw-checkout-map.js`, wrap everything under a single namespace:

```javascript
window.ALW = window.ALW || {};
(function(ALW, config) {
    ALW.map = null;
    ALW.markers = {};
    // ... all logic
})(window.ALW, window.alw_config);
```

### 3.3 Internationalization (i18n)

#### [MODIFY] All PHP files

Wrap every user-facing string with [__()](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping.php#6-13) or `esc_html__()`:

```diff
- wc_add_notice( 'We do not deliver to this address...', 'error' );
+ wc_add_notice( sprintf(
+     __( 'We do not deliver to this address — it is %.2f km away which exceeds our delivery radius of %s km.', 'auto-location-woocommerce' ),
+     $distance_km, ALW_MAX_KM
+ ), 'error' );
```

JS strings will use `alw_config.i18n.string_key` passed from `wp_localize_script()`.

### 3.4 Hardcoded Currency Fix

#### [MODIFY] Frontend JS (new `alw-checkout-map.js`)

```diff
- shippingText = 'Shipping: ₹' + calc.cost;
+ shippingText = config.i18n.shipping_label + ': ' + config.currency + calc.cost;
```

