## Phase 4: Advanced Features — `v2.0.0`

### 4.1 Distance Brackets / Tiered Pricing

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-shipping-method.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-shipping-method.php)

Add a repeater-style settings field for distance tiers:

| From (km) | To (km) | Rate per KM | Flat Fee |
|-----------|---------|-------------|----------|
| 0 | 5 | 0 | 0 (Free) |
| 5 | 15 | 10 | 0 |
| 15 | 30 | 15 | 50 |

Store as serialized array in instance settings. The `calculate_shipping()` method will look up the appropriate tier.

### 4.2 Admin Map Picker for Store Coordinates

#### [MODIFY] [class-alw-admin.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-admin.php)

#### [NEW] [alw-admin-map.js](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/assets/js/alw-admin-map.js)

Embed a small Google Map in the admin settings page where the admin can:
- Click the map to set store coordinates
- Use "My Location" to auto-fill coordinates
- See a visual confirmation of the selected point

Auto-populate the lat/lng fields when the map pin is moved.

### 4.3 Address Autocomplete (Places API)

#### [MODIFY] [alw-checkout-map.js](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/assets/js/alw-checkout-map.js)

Add Google Places Autocomplete to the `billing_address_1` field. When a suggestion is selected:
1. Extract lat/lng from the Place result
2. Pan the map to that location
3. Trigger distance recalculation

### 4.4 Delivery Radius Visualization

#### [MODIFY] [alw-checkout-map.js](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/assets/js/alw-checkout-map.js)

Draw a semi-transparent circle on the map centered on the store with `radius = MAX_KM * 1000` meters. This gives the customer a visual cue of the delivery zone.

