## Phase 5: Future-Proofing — `v2.1.0`

### 5.1 WooCommerce Blocks Checkout Support

#### [NEW] [src/](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/src/)

Create a React-based block integration:
- `src/checkout-block/index.js` — Register a checkout block integration
- `src/checkout-block/frontend.js` — The map component for the Blocks checkout
- Use `@woocommerce/blocks-checkout` package and `registerCheckoutBlock()`
- Integrate with the Store API via `ExtendSchema`

#### [NEW] [class-alw-blocks-integration.php](file:///d:/Z_Work/Sayan/sugar%20story/auto-location-woocommerce/includes/class-alw-blocks-integration.php)

PHP-side integration:
- Implement `Automattic\WooCommerce\Blocks\Integrations\IntegrationInterface`
- Register block scripts and pass config to the frontend

### 5.2 Multi-Store Origin Support

#### [MODIFY] Admin Settings / Shipping Method

- Allow defining multiple store/warehouse origins with individual coordinates
- The shipping calculation picks the **closest origin** to the customer to calculate the rate
- Each origin can have its own delivery radius and pricing rules

### 5.3 Delivery Scheduling (Stretch)

- Add a date/time picker to checkout
- Define delivery windows (e.g., 9am–12pm, 2pm–6pm)
- Optional surcharge for express/off-hours delivery

